snippet.title: Frantis: Mission II gameplay (PC Game, 1993)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Frantis: Mission II (aka megadestroyer frantis 2), Dos PC game produced by Anonymous in 1993 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/frantis-mission-ii/13104/
Frantis: Mission II is an exciting game, like SCI-FI, with plenty of action and shooting.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Impossible Mission 2 - https://youtu.be/6stdL-0b3U0
